SUMMARY:Salsa Bachata Friday and Saturday at The Granada
DESCRIPTION:Salsa Bachata Friday and Saturday at The Granada. The Granada functions as a nightclub\, dance studio\, restaurant and bar\, and typically offers three floors for dancing salsa\, bachata\, merengue\, reggaeton and more. Classes\, socials and concerts usually go from 7:30pm to 3am. \nCheck The Granada website for a complete list of their events!
